## Quick Start Commands

### Server Deployment:
```bash
cd server/
chmod +x deploy.sh
./deploy.sh deploy
```

### Client Installation:
```bash
# Windows: run scripts/install_client.bat
# Linux/macOS: chmod +x scripts/install_client.sh && ./scripts/install_client.sh
```

### Portable Build:
```bash
# Windows: run scripts/build_portable.bat
# Linux/macOS: chmod +x scripts/build_portable.sh && ./scripts/build_portable.sh
# Manual: python scripts/build_portable.py
```

### Development:
```bash
# Start server manually
cd server/ && python start_server.py

# Start client
python bin/main.py

# Combined startup (client + server)
python bin/start_all.py
```

